Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.67,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.08,0:01:41.02,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson Is Taken Hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:06.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You took so many photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.99,0:02:08.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all of Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will see this thing\Nthrough to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the criminal's way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:18.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I will explain\Nthe entire operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:23.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've had to endure so many things\Nbecause of our hated enemy, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thoroughly beaten us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:31.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Our urgent task is to defeat Holmes\Nand recover our honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:33.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent task?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:33.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been thinking of ways\Nto beat that cunning young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:41.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many flies in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:44.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:45.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.03,0:02:50.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been observing Holmes\Nclosely to find his weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:52.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've finally found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:56.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at his eyes!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:00.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:02.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:07.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is giving those\Neyes to only one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:10.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:15.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know her! I know this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:17.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Mary Hudson. She's a widow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:18.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nineteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:21.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She is the owner of the boarding\Nhouse where Holmes staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:23.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want to have this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what are you\Ngoing to do professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kidnap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:32.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnap?! This woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:36.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice\Nif we are to defeat Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:37.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.58,0:03:40.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You are planning to marry\Nher after you kidnap her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:41.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:43.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you are so dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You turned red!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:02.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, another chemistry experiment?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't suggest going\Nin there for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is a letter, it just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:11.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I hope this is a request\Nfor an investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:14.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:16.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a letter.\NI just made a simple deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a doorbell just before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:25.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, why don't you stop\Nthis useless experimentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My brain would begin\Nto rot without work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Car loan, a bill from the\Nliquor shop and the drug store.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watson! It's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:41.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:48.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going some place?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not such a big case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:15.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Mr. Holmes live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:16.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:17.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, carry it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:22.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our finest coffin\Nthat you ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but this must be\Nsome kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:32.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It matches the height perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:34.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose height?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:39.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:54.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, beautiful.\NJust like Snow White.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the air hole open?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:58.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.41,0:06:18.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a poor joke.\NSending us a fake letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:19.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:23.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the plant Mrs. Hudson\Nwas holding when we left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still smell\Nsome tranquillizer here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes! Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:45.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes, I took Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:50.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you care for her safety,\Nwait quietly for further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:56.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He wrote that fake letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:01.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do Holmes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to wait\Nfor him to contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:17.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!\NThe drug will wear off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But she still hasn't woken up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:27.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pest you are!\NI said she's just sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:33.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.75,0:07:34.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.95,0:07:36.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't accuse me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My murders have never\Nbeen successful before!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:41.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:44.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.53,0:07:46.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Just stop it!\NIt's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die after I kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:51.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:53.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She came back to life. I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:01.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I... what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:03.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See! I told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.49,0:08:07.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:09.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring coffee or brandy.\NNo, bring both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:12.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We better not talk back to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:14.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:20.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you Madam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.37,0:08:24.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like there's a\Nfatal oversight to this plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:25.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:28.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this brandy is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.64,0:08:31.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I had it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a very expensive brandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:34.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know there's another\None inside your bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd he know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:43.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kidnapped?\NAm I being kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You are my prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:49.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you behave,\NI won't take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would you prefer?\NCoffee or brandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:54.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'd like to have brandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.27,0:08:57.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please help yourself,\Nbut it's not an expensive one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:08:59.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's you name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.37,0:09:04.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She said I'm a good person!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:06.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:08.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:10.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:16.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my secret hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how loud you scream,\Nnobody will come to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a wife, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.57,0:09:27.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.93,0:09:29.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would want such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:40.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this place so dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:48.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I have to stay here a while,\Ncan I clean up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:52.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up? I'm a busy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time\Nto do housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.93,0:09:56.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make any trouble for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:59.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, could you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:01.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll be happy to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this going to be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.78,0:10:13.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past the time\Nwe were supposed to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.58,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.92,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the phone Mr. Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:24.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A thread phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.26,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What are your terms, Moriarty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! You are so submissive, Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:35.03,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:37.40,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to do one task for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:41.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,By tomorrow, I want you to steal\Nfamous portrait, La Giconda...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:45.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,now on exhibit\Nat the National Gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And you want to\Nexchange it for Mrs. Hudson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a very attractive woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.52,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that losing her\Nwould be a great loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.46,0:11:04.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Busy! Busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.80,0:11:11.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.24,0:11:16.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I received this letter just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:16.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.78,0:11:19.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's just some complaint...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,like the neighbour's cat\Nis making too much noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"I am going to steal the\Nmasterpiece La Giconda's..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.65,0:11:29.68,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"from the National Gallery, tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:33.82,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's no use trying to guard it.\NS.H."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:41.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?! This smell's like...\Npipe tobacco and chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.39,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll have a drink\Nand go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:11.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I come back to the wrong house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:15.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you already home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! E... Excuse me but what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotten a little cleaner,\Nhasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll serve dinner right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:24.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please put your hat\Nand coat on the rack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:33.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:39.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you will like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Great! Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the smell of kidney pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:05.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Smiley told me\Nthat you love kidney pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:07.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,T... Then did you make this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:15.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.\NYou have a stomach-ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:21.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm touched!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:24.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... the first time anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:34.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But a game is a game.\NI can't loosen up my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:36.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I know my situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:38.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Work is work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:42.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please eat this.\NI've made many more dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.12,0:13:46.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:49.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! Tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Win, lose, win, lose, win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:04.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Lose, win, lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... win!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:14.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:17.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:20.59,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I must beat Holmes this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:25.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just launching a surprise\Nattack on the National Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:29.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.27,0:14:33.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to win!\NI will absolutely win this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:49.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How is everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:49.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no sign of movement, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been like that\Nfor the last three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:15:00.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's just a phony letter,\Nbut just to make sure, keep watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:01.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.03,0:15:04.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anyone else\Nleft the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:07.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,An old couple came\Nout a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:07.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:11.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:14.31,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.45,0:15:15.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you read the original work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:25.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:27.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Place guards all around the museum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:28.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:33.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that detective watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:35.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's working for Lestrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.47,0:15:37.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty must have tipped them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wants to get the portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:42.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, what he really wants\Nis to get me arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anything happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:05.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many police.\NHolmes might have a difficult time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:33.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:40.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:41.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:44.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There are rats!\NComing out all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:45.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:54.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:57.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He left a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.01,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll hide this for a little while."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:02.15,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please don't worry.\NI will return it by tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:05.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I not worry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:08.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:14.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If you move even an inch,\NI will arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:19.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The thief must be hiding here.\NI will check them all one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:30.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The portrait isn't small,\Nso it's not so easy to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the last man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.58,0:17:35.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already checked all the women,\Nbut we couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I think I've\Nseen you somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:41.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:44.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:57.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to get\Ninto that coffin again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:18:00.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, after that, I will take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be another trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:03.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be arriving shortly at the\Nlocation they designated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:11.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent!\NThis time I'll catch the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:23.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the portrait as I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Mrs. Hudson?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:31.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:36.71,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me see the beauty\Nthat you brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:45.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the greatest treasure\Nin all history... the Mona Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:49.92,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of outrageous\Nthing did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You acted just like a thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my god!\NThe Detective stole the portrait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.30,0:18:58.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.54,0:19:03.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:06.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There is the thief who\Nstole the famous portrait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked me Moriarty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.78,0:19:10.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You are under arrest\Nfor art theft!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:12.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say I tricked you.\NPeople might think it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You villain! Moriarty, you\Nhave the mind of an eggplant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can\Nget away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:22.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the line I wanted to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, it's broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to that\Ntreasure of all mankind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:39.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain to him, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:44.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I just stood in front of the empty\Nframe with amazement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:49.01,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But the painting was merely\Ncovered by a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the back of\Nthe paper was a note...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:53.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,with the entire account\Nof this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.46,0:19:56.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This portrait is a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:59.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:02.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:03.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:10.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent Holmes,\Nbut you haven't won just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The hostage is in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you going to jump\Nthe river to get her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he still doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:18.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:22.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This river is so shallow,\Neven a child can cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.72,0:20:23.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:27.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I can\Nsee fish swimming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:31.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:50.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:51.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.92,0:20:52.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:55.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!\NHang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go around! Go around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:18.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, you didn't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:24.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I really should take you home,\Nbut I have to say goodbye here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.18,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If I ever have the chance,\Nwe can see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:34.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had met you earlier, my life\Nwould have changed for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.29,0:21:37.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But I promise one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.26,0:21:40.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never let you become\Ninvolved in my work again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.83,0:21:41.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:46.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my treasure,\Nbut I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:46.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you my marble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:52.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:56.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:03.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:04.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.06,0:22:06.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.16,0:22:08.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.19,0:22:09.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have had an awful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:10.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:15.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:20.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time I've had\Nsomething so worth cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:22.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
