Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.47,0:24:00.06,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,In the sky over London, a monster\Nbird "Steramadon" appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.30,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,The public square was in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.41,0:24:04.87,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Moriarty took\Nadvantage of the chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:10.54,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,and stole the blue ruby,\Nthe only one of it's kind in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.42,0:24:16.98,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
